definitions.definition: A village and civil parish (served by Allerston and Wilton Parish Council) in Ryedale district, North Yorkshire , England ( OS grid ref SE8782 ) .
A community in the County of Warner No. 5, Alberta , Canada , named after Jacob Allers.
